Body: Official BOUNTY THREAD  Korean ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4699950  Russian ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3458575  Japanese ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4766651  India ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4712125  Portuguese ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4683109  Spanish ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4670963  German ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4686146  Arabic ANN Thread    https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4701899   Brief introduction to the project.      The GeoManna platform is a decentralized, socially funded ecosystem for direct peer-to-peer interaction (P2P - peer to peer). Transparency, reliability, speed and equal opportunities are the core values embodied in the technology of blocking and the functionality of a smart contract on a platform.      The platform expands the potential of using financial services on the basis of a distributed registry, self-executing smart contracts.      The GeoManna ecosystem is designed to unite all participants in one place, providing them with a platform for creating and using financial services, where everyone can, and offer a service, and use it.      GeoManna is able to offer a new technical solution and a new conceptual model of interaction between platform participants for the development of modern decentralized financial services.       The GeoManna platform will be friendly and with a minimum of technical terminology to offer services to the general public, indicating the benefits and capabilities of the platform.      The GeoManna platform is a New World in which users create values themselves.   What are the existing problems we plan to solve?     All existing models of the modern economy are no longer effective. High interest rates and transfer fees, as well as low speed, hamper the normal development of business and consumer relationships, as well as their accumulative abilities.      Concentration of funds in one hand breaks the balance and hinders the competitiveness of business, conditioned by old approaches that do not work in the modern world.      The situation in the world economy is complicated, and social tension only increases. These are clear signs of a distant departure from the path of normal social development.      The difficulties of the modern economy and the lack of clear ways to overcome them make development in the direction of block technology.      Existing latest technological developments can solve the problems of the modern economy, but they are reluctant to accept old established systems.      The single technological decentralized platform GeoManna is able to unite all participants of financial services, safely and quickly execute all transactions that operate on the principles of the distributed registry. Bonus name: GeoManna Bonus Symbol: GM Period of validity of the bonus: 10 years Bonus release environment: platform Ethereum Standard of issue of a bonus: the smart contract corresponding to the standard Ethereum ERC-20 The number of decimal places in the bonus: 2 Currencies of sale of the bonus: Ethereum (ETH) The standard price at the time of the release of the bonus: 1 GM = 0,10 USD Minimum target volume of pre-sales equivalent to 300 (ETH) Maximum sales limit: not limited The number of GM bonuses issued for the pre-sales phase 100 000 000 Minimum purchase volume: equivalent to 0.1 (ETH) Sales start date: beginning August 1, 2018. Sales end date: Novemder 1, 2018. All not sold bonuses at the end of all stages of sales will be burned.  Referral program At all stages of pre-Sales, the referral program will be. And everyone can get a profit by attracting investments. To participate in the referral program, register at geomanna.com In your account, copy the referral link and send it to the investors. You will be credited with 10% of the amount purchased by your referrals GeoManna.   Platform capabilities.     Mass adaptation of the GeoManna platform to improve the effectiveness of all relationships between people and business, eliminating any intermediaries from these relationships and making their interactions transparent, safe and profitable. This solution will be achieved through the creation of a decentralized ecosystem, based on the optimized bandwidth of the block and the organization of interaction between users on the principle of P2P (peer-to-peer).      Technological innovations in the field of computer technology combine the capabilities of payment systems and will improve the existing model of interaction between the supplier and the consumer. A number of integrated solutions and methods of contactless instant transfers will exclude commissions, which will increase the purchasing power of consumers. At the same time, the use of fixed cost is ideal for the consumer and corporate sectors of the economy. The balance of the number of bonuses inside the platform will not be violated and on the direct will depend on their relevance. In other words, the participants themselves encourage the creation of new bonuses by method Proof-of-Activity (PoA). More participants, more bonuses.   The GeoManna platform will allow: ‚Ä¢  Integrate your business into a platform and make profit and new customers. ‚Ä¢  Exchange goods, services and entertainment for bonuses. ‚Ä¢  Become part of the platform in a particular branch of the structure. ‚Ä¢  To use the wide possibilities of blockchain technology and the industry as a whole! ‚Ä¢  Continuous improvement of development and other advanced technologies. ‚Ä¢  Search for like-minded people to implement and launch the project around the world.   Advantages     The GeoManna platform, in itself, is unique and has no analogues. Absolute absence of competitors will allow the platform to dynamically develop, and the bonus of GM is firmly entrenched among the leading crypto assets.      GeoManna will enable any user regardless of technical knowledge to easily access the platform and information. After installing the mobile application, any user can watch how GM bonuses enter his pocket. Users themselves make decisions about the relevance of the platform by using it.      Almost all cryptocurrencies require special equipment for mining. You do not need to earn GeoManna bonuses, you get them for free. GeoManna develops a fully functional bonus with some unique features:  - The instant money transfer system is safe and anonymous;  - Absence of commission for all users of the platform;  - Possibility of storage and accumulation with full control over funds;  - Global access to trading sites and services.           On which national platforms is the project oriented?      At the start of the project, all information will be available in the main languages. As the project develops for ease of use, more languages will be added.      Multilanguage and accessibility - contributes to global expansion.      The project is focused on the whole world.
